metadata.name: Sakura Mossy
metadata.description:
Mossy loves to visit Japan for the lush moss gardens, fascinating culture and to enjoy the eye catching floral explosions of Cherry Blossom season. A little Shima Enaga has perched on Mossy's head as Bigby the Bee flies by on a beautiful day in Japan.

Upon primary sale this 1/1 is bundled with the held back edition #1 of 25  sold out physical "Sakura Mossy" hand-painted & flocked vinyl toys. Illustrated with Procreate & Photoshop.

4000 px x 4000 px at 300 dpi
